<section class="hero">
  <div class="content">
    <h1>WELCOME<br>STEFAN</h1>
    <p>We've prepared a special journey through our remarkable highlights of the year. Buckle up for an exciting retrospective of our finest moments in the automotive world.</p>
    <button class="cta">TAKE A RIDE THROUGH THE HIGHLIGHTS</button>
  </div>
  <div class="image">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://www.carauktion.ch/img/logo@2x.png" alt="Car Auktion Logo" />
    </div>
    <dotlottie-player 
      src="https://lottie.host/f79752c1-2e24-48c3-97e1-175e5fe438b2/MwIA5KtOCG.lottie" 
      background="transparent" 
      speed="1" 
      loop 
      autoplay
    ></dotlottie-player>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
  }

  .content {
    padding: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--brand-red);
  }

  h1 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 80%;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta {
    background: white;
    color: var(--brand-red);
    border: none;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: fit-content;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .image {
    background: white;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .logo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2rem;
    height: 40px;
  }

  .logo img {
    height: 100%;
    width: auto;
  }

  .image dotlottie-player {
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
  }
</style>